<item>
            <title>[LU-10583] replay-single tests failing due to &#8216;error: readonly: Operation not supported&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10583</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Several replay-single tests are failing with a variety of error messages, but the same error is seen in all the suite log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: trevis-6vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl --device lustre-MDT0000 readonly
trevis-6vm4: error: readonly: Operation not supported
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue is only seen on the lustre-master-patchless branch/builds. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For any one test session, different replay-single tests fail with not being able to set the MDT to readonly. Some of these tests are 0c, 44c, 70b, 80d, 81a, 81d, and 120. In addition, replay-vbr tests 1b,2b, 3b, 4c, 4d, 4f, 4h, 5b, 5c, 6c, 6d, 7a, 7b, 7c, 7e, 7f, 7h, 7i, 10b, 12a and conf-sanity test 84 fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logs for recent failures are at:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7e248094-0351-11e8-bd00-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7e248094-0351-11e8-bd00-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/137ebe96-0359-11e8-bd00-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/137ebe96-0359-11e8-bd00-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
